ure normalization, but that alone did not close the `TestPoint` mismatch yet. The immediate next target I would take is the clustered hierarchy-label regression family (`issue10926_1_subsheet_1_1`, `issue14657_2`, `issue18606_child_test`, `top_level_hier_pins`), because those failures all show the same local pattern: missing upstream `isolated_pin_label`/subsheet label projection on standalone or shallow hierarchical roots."}],"phase":"commentary"}}
