esses non-primary sibling instance refs, matching KiCad’s shared-sheet reporting for `netlists/hierarchical_component_classes/hierarchical_component_classes.kicad_sch`.\n- In [root.rs](/Users/Daniel/Desktop/modular/tools/ki-erc-refactor-wt/src/cmd/schematic/erc/rules/root.rs), root `isolated_pin_label` now accounts for sheet pins as real pin-like connections, which closed `netlists/test_global_promotion_2/test_global_promotion_2.kicad_sch`.\n\nPromotions added:\n- [instance_params](/Users/Daniel/Desktop/modular/tools/ki-erc-refactor-wt/tests/cli_schematic_erc.rs)\n- [hierarchical_component_classes](/Users/Daniel/Desktop/modular/tools/ki-erc-refactor-wt/tests/cli_schematic_erc.rs)\n- [test_global_promotion_2](/Users/Daniel/Desktop/modular/tools/ki-erc-refactor-wt/tests/cli_schematic_erc.rs)\n- [manifest.json](/Users/Daniel/Desktop/modular/tools/ki-erc-refactor-wt/tests/fixtures/erc_upstream_qa/manifest.json)\n\nVerification that passed:\n- `schematic_erc_matches_upstream_instance_params_fixture`\n- `schematic_erc_matches_upstream_hierarchical_component_classes_fixture_exactly`\n- `schematic_erc_matches_upstream_hierarchical_component_classes_another_sheet_fixture`\n- `schematic_erc_matches_upstream_test_global_promotion_2_fixture_exactly`\n- `schematic_erc_matches_upstream_test_global_promotion_2_subsheet_fixture`\n- `erc_parity_cases_manifest_is_well_formed`\n\nCurrent maintained upstream-QA exact count is `138`. Working tree is clean apart from the existing untracked `.codex/` and `.entire/`.\n\nNext real live backlog from the refreshed frontier is still around:\n- `issue21980/issue21980.kicad_sch`\n- `issue13162.kicad_sch`\n- `issue12814.kicad_sch`\n\n`netlists/test_global_promotion/test_global_promotion.kicad_sch` remains ambiguous upstream behavior: live `kicad-cli` omits a `C1` footprint-filter warning even though the schematic and current `Device:C` filter surface both still suggest it should exist, so I did not force a local suppression."}],"phase":"final_ans