{"timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:59:13.723Z","type":"event_msg","payload":{"type":"agent_message","message":"`issue14657` exposed one more hole in the same hierarchy surface: I was only suppressing child hierarchical-label projection for bus-member exports, but KiCad also suppresses the direct sheet-pin export case when the child net actually carries the signal to a local pin. I’m tightening that now, along with the small cleanup from the root-label patch.","phase":"commentary","memory_citation":null}}
